Conditions:
CD688: (Conditions) The release of consignments into free circulation shall be subject to the presentation by the feed or food business operator to the custom authorities of a CED duly completed by the competent authority once all official controls have been carried out. The CED may be presented physically or electronically.
Exemptions apply in accordance with Article 1 (3) of Regulation (EU) No 2015/175.
